    "Name": "Lobo",
    "Details": "This version of the Lobo replaces the standard weaponry with a large pulse laser, two ER medium lasers, two AP Gauss rifles, and two plasma cannons. This makes it an effective anti-infantry and anti-battle armor 'Mech. It also adds one extra double heat sink to the configuration.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - Laser</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>",
